data.description: More pictures coming soon! Maintenance free living in this maintained townhome. Perfectly located in the quiet Rock Springs Estate Subdivision. This home includes three bedrooms, three baths, a fenced yard & a two car attached garage. Master suite has a full bath and walk in close, with a family room conveniently located just off the master bedroom. No HOA.
